fields.name: Cariboo classic bassinet
fields.description:
The Classic Bassinet is a substantial piece of furniture. The comprehensive design and detailed safety features continue to uphold the Cariboo Classic Bassinet as one of the very best bassinets available. 
Suitable for newborns up to approximately five months old, or until they start rolling over or pulling themselves up.

fields.name: Graco Evo pushchair stroller
fields.description:
The Graco Evo pushchair stroller is suitable from birth and converts from a lie flat pram to a fully reversible seat. From birth to approx. 3 years (0 - 15 kg)
• Fully reversible toddler seat, forward or rear facing with three-position seat back recline to full lie flat
• Convenient one hand fold and extra large shopping basket
• One-Click travel system allows you to team with the  Junior Baby 
• Includes raincover and footmuff

fields.name: Dr. Brown's Bottle Warmer
fields.description:
Made in USA and Imported
Warms standard and wide neck baby bottles and baby food jars
Refillable water chamber warms several bottles before refilling
LCD control panel is easy to read and set for memorizing heating time
Audible alarm with flashing LCD lets you know when ready
Cycle memory repeats preferred heating time

fields.name: Owl Graco Woodland 3Pc Baby Girl Crib Bedding Set by Kidsline Nursery Newborn
fields.description:
The Girl Woodland 3 Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set includes a quilt, dust ruffle and fitted sheet.

The quilt measures 33 inches x 42 inches.

The dust ruffle has a 12 inch drop and the fitted sheet is made to fit a standard size 28 inch x 52 inch crib mattress.

The fitted sheet is made of 100% cotton.

The quilt and dust ruffle are made of 100% polyester and 65% polyester-35% cotton fabrics. Filling is 100% polyester.

fields.name: 25 Preschool Kindergarten Childrens Picture Book Grade 1 2 AR Reader Teacher Lot
fields.description:
Popular children's classic picture books  for preschool/kidergarten or grade 1-2 in accelerated or guided reading.  Many popular authors - Patricia Polacco, Leo Lionni, Denise Fleming, Marc Brown, Bill Martin, Jonathan London, and Mercer Mayer.  Most are on the AR reading list and I have listed the book levels and points. The first three are more appropriate for read-aloud. Books have this info penciled in front cover. These are mostly paperback books and two hardbacks. 

Most are in very good condition, and a few have some normal edge wear and corner bends. They all have nice clean pages with rich color pictures and I saw no writing or tears to pages, just a few bends. A few have sticker remnants and most have names in covers. No noticable odors.

fields.name: Walnut Rocking Horse
fields.description: The finest quality walnut wood gives the Premium rocking horse a wonderfully warm appearance with its natural chocolate brown color. To complement the natural rich color of the wood, only real horsehair in natural colors is used to finish the horse. Furthermore, the finest leatherwork is selected to make the saddle and bridle, maintaining a high quality standard to ensure high expectations are satisfied.

fields.name: BouncePro 14' Trampoline with Steelflex Enclosure and Electron Shooter Game, Dark Blue
fields.description: This BouncePro 14-foot trampoline with the patented Electron Shooter is the perfect addition to any backyard area. The Bonus Electron Shooter target attaches easily to the enclosure ring, creating extra play value for kids. The galvanized steel frame and UV-resistant jump mat will provide years of safe and fun entertainment. The Steel Flex Safety Enclosure features padded poles for extra protection, UV-resistant PE netting and a steel-cabled ring top to add additional support to the enclosure. The spring-loading tool makes it easier and safer to attach the springs to the mat. BouncePro trampolines come with a 2-year warranty with product registration.

fields.name: Jeep X16 Boys Full Suspension Bike 16" bicycle orange w training wheels kids NEW
fields.description:
The rugged Jeep 16" Boys Bike comes equipped with a real suspension frame and fork that soak up bumps, big or small. This boys bike is simple to put together as it comes with an easy to understand instructions kit. This Jeep bicycle is available in a striking combination of bright orange and black and just looks amazing on roads. This full suspension bike has thicker training wheels that will let your young champ enjoy a safe and comfortable ride. With coaster and front hand brakes, he can quickly, easily, and safely brake even on those rough and uneven surfaces. In short, the Jeep 16" Boys Bike is a good quality bike and is recommended for children aged between 5 and 8 years.



Jeep 16" Boys Bike with Full Suspension:
Frame: suspension frame
CPSC full wrap chain charge
Brakes: coaster brake and front hand brake
Dimensions: 45"L x 22"W x 31"H
